      "id": "PopularPost64159",
      "post_content": "Cheza, for you to be concerned for mind control to be forbidden by law sounds to me like you are a little on the White side of Blue.   \nEach color, having two allied colors, has spells that seem a bit on either side of itself, as well as purely that color.   \n  \nFor example, Black has spells that seem a bit more Red, (straightforward destruction or killing, like [Sinkhole](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sinkhole).) and some that seem a bit more Blue (Deceptive and Manipulative in nature like [Head Games](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Head Games)).   \n  \nSince Blue is in-between White and Black, it takes a neutral standpoint in terms of morality. Both an evil mastermind and a fair judge could use Blue magic for their own unique purposes, to get their own way with someone or to divulge the truth to bring about justice respectively.   \n  \nHope that helped.",
      "posted_by": "Blackworm_Bloodworm",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost64159\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Cheza, for you to be concerned for mind control to be forbidden by law sounds to me like you are a little on the White side of Blue. <br/>Each color, having two allied colors, has spells that seem a bit on either side of itself, as well as purely that color. <br/><br/>For example, Black has spells that seem a bit more Red, (straightforward destruction or killing, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sinkhole\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sinkhole\">Sinkhole</a>.) and some that seem a bit more Blue (Deceptive and Manipulative in nature like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Head Games\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Head Games\">Head Games</a>). <br/><br/>Since Blue is in-between White and Black, it takes a neutral standpoint in terms of morality. Both an evil mastermind and a fair judge could use Blue magic for their own unique purposes, to get their own way with someone or to divulge the truth to bring about justice respectively. <br/><br/>Hope that helped.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '64159'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy29658\">Blackworm_Bloodworm</span>\r\n                                (4/10/20